data.description: WOW!  Super convenient location for this updated 2 Bedroom condo. Drive into one of your TWO heated garage stalls and walk just a few steps down the hallway to your condo. Fresh paint, new stove, microwave, dishwasher and lighting. Generous sized primary bedroom has huge walk in closet and private half bath.  Close to 494, 35, and American Blvd. Enjoy all the nearby amenities...public transportation, shopping, restaurants, entertainment, parks and schools. Close in time to enjoy the shared, heated, in-ground pool this summer, steps away from your patio!
